POST http://localhost:4000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vikas.author@example.com",
  "password": "Author@12345"
  
}



### Create article (AUTHOR)
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author":"69af9844332e4fcb68fc6491",
  "title":"test2 article",
  "category":"programming",
  "content":"content of test2 article"
}



###Read articles of an author
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69af9844332e4fcb68fc6491



### Update article (AUTHOR)
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author":"69af9844332e4fcb68fc6491",
  "articleId":"69af986f332e4fcb68fc6496",
  "title":"test2 article updated",
  "category":"programming",
  "content":"content of test2 article updated"
}



### Delete article
PATCH http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69af986f332e4fcb68fc6496/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "isArticleActive": true }


### Logout
GET http://localhost:4000/common-api/logout



### Change password
PUT http://localhost:4000/common-api/change-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":"test@example.com",
  "currentPassword":"test",
  "newPassword":"test1"
  
}